how to setup:
go to root folder and type
>  sudo npm install

then go to /public and type
> bower install


copy the datatables files:
bower_components/datatables/media folder   to  /libs/datatables
bower_components/dataTables.bootstrap.css/index.css  to  /libs/datatables/media/css
 and rename to dataTables.bootstrap.css
bower_components/dataTables.bootstrap.js/index.js  to  /libs/datatables/media/js
 and rename to dataTables.bootstrap.js
 

Error handling:
is done via global call to
fbtrading.handleError